   Mayor Ed Koch said he learned ``moonwalking''
from singer Michael Jackson, and now he's going to strut his stuff.
   At an impromptu news conference Wednesday at City Hall, Koch
promised to moonwalk in Saturday's Inner Circle show, an annual
