haberdasher, lives just outside New York in Greenwich, Conn., he
makes no secret of his love for North Carolina.
   He's designing uniforms for the Charlotte Hornets, a new
National Basketball Association franchise. For that work, Julian is
being paid 10 pounds of North Carolina barbecue, delivered once a
month to his New York office.
