acrobatic tigers and a quadruple somersault by the Cranes aerialist
troupe.
   The troupe has not appeared in North America since 1978, with
U.S.-Soviet cultural exchanges frozen after the 1979 Soviet
invasion of Afghanistan.
   For New York area ticket information call: 212 757-3100.
Elsewhere: 800 882-5696.
